om-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: dotted; margin: 0px; padding: 16px 0px =
5px;">Trump SPAC</h2>
</td>
</tr>
</table><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Donald Trump is a very famous person w=
ho likes to talk and who has a lot of enthusiastic fans. If he started a te=
levision channel that consisted of=C2=A0him talking about whatever for two =
hours every afternoon, surrounded by 22 hours of other people talking about=
 how great he is, it would probably get a lot of viewers and could carry a =
lot of ads for pillows or whatever. But this would probably involve a certa=
in amount=C2=A0of work and competence =E2=80=94=C2=A0you=E2=80=99d have to =
hire people to point the cameras at him and negotiate cable carriage and ad=
 deals =E2=80=94 and television is expensive; there would be some real fina=
ncial risk to it.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Or he could start a socia=
l media company for his fans, where he could send out his thoughts without =
being banned. I am not going to pretend to make a business case for that on=
e =E2=80=94=C2=A0there is a long=C2=A0<a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloomber=
gbusiness.com/click/25418633.268044/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cud2lyZWQuY29tL3N0b3J5L2d=
hYi1oYWNrLWRhdGEtYnJlYWNoLWRkb3NlY3JldHMv/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB3c212145=
" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D=
"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px=
; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-colo=
r: #ccc;"></a><a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/2541=
8633.268044/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cubnl0aW1lcy5jb20vMjAyMS8wMS8wOS90ZWNobm9sb2d5L2F=
