, Helvetica, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -1px; font-size: 20px; border-bott=
om-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: dotted; margin: 0px; padding: 16px 0px =
5px;">Compass</h2>
</td>
</tr>
</table><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Speaking of the sort of person I am, I=
 was not able to do the Compass puzzle hunt last weekend but I was very sor=
ry to miss it. Here is a <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com=
/click/25418633.268044/aHR0cHM6Ly9ueXBvc3QuY29tLzIwMjEvMTAvMTkvd2FsbC1zdHJl=
ZXRzLWNpdHktd2lkZS1wdXp6bGUtY29tcGFzcy1yYWlzZXMtb3Zlci0xbS1mb3ItY2hhcml0eS8=
/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB10aefeff" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"ite=
